% Disease and recommended diet
diet(diabetes, 'Eat more vegetables, whole grains, avoid sugar').
diet(hypertension, 'Reduce salt intake, avoid oily food, eat fruits').
diet(obesity, 'Low calorie diet, more salads, avoid junk food').
diet(anemia, 'Iron-rich food like spinach, beetroot, jaggery').
diet(cold, 'Vitamin C rich food like orange, lemon, amla').

% Rule
suggest_diet(Disease, Diet) :- diet(Disease, Diet).
